<HEADLINE>
FT  05 JAN 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
A LOWER bullion price depressed sentiment as the gold index lost 13 to 786,
the overall index fell 7 to 3,252 and industrials weakened 4 to 4,359. De
Beers bucked the easier trend, adding 25 cents at R57.75.
