</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   PARIS
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
CLUB Mediterranee, the French holiday village group, reported a 4.8 per cent
rise in turnover to FFr8.22bn (Dollars 1.48bn) in the year to last October,
despite the gloom in the travel industry.
The group released its turnover figures yesterday, a month after publishing
