crossihg, upgrading the route from single to dual carriageway.
Operating from bases in Wolverhampton, Manchester and Newbury, Tarmac
Regional Civil Engineering was created earlier this year to tackle works up
to Pounds 10m.
Larger schemes are undertaken by its sister organisation, Tarmac's major
projects division.
