<TEXT>
France's education minister, Mr Jack Lang, yesterday ordered schools and
universities to shelter the homeless from a week-old cold spell that has
killed seven people, reports Reuter from Paris. Temperatures have dropped
below freezing throughout France, reaching minus 15 Celsius in places.
