FT  04 JAN 93 / (CORRECTED) Life in the Single Market: A hitchhiker's guide
 -If you want to know more . . .
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Correction (published 5th January 1993) appended to this article.
READING LIST
You've read all about it - now it's time to see if you can play the game. A
new Europe is open for business and there are advantages to be won. But
there are new rules to be followed if you are not to miss a turn or end up
back at go. This directory guides businesses, especially small and
medium-sized companies, through a Euromaze
Influencing the European Community - Guidelines for a Successful Business
Strategy. By Cecilia Andersen. 358 pages. Pounds 35. Kogan Page. 120
Pentonville Road, London N1 9JN. Tel: 071 278 0433. A guide to lobbying with
a wealth of background information on how the community works.
