The address for Cenelec, the European Committee for Electrotechnical
Standardisation, was incorrect in yesterday's issue. It is Rue de Stassart
35, B-1050, Brussels, Tel (322) 519 6871. CEN, the European Committee for
Standardisation, is at Rue de Stassart 36, B-1050, Brussels, Tel 519 6811.
